sequenceDiagram
    participant Operator as rhods-operator
    participant Kustomize as Kustomize Build
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Registry as registry.redhat.io<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Gateway as OpenShift Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.3
    participant RBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Jupyter as JupyterLab<br/>8888/TCP HTTP
    participant Nginx as nginx<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant HTTPD as httpd CGI<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant CodeSrv as Code-Server<br/>8787/TCP HTTP
    participant Culler as Notebook Controller<br/>Culler

    Note over Operator,Registry: Flow 1: Image Deployment via Operator
    Operator->>Kustomize: Read manifests/rhoai/overlays/
    Kustomize->>Kustomize: Build ConfigMap notebook-image-params<br/>Apply kustomize replacements
    Kustomize-->>Operator: Rendered ImageStream manifests
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Apply ImageStreams<br/>HTTPS/6443, ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI->>Registry: Import images by digest<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+, Pull secret

    Note over User,Jupyter: Flow 2: User Workbench Access (RHOAI 3.x)
    User->>Gateway: GET /notebook/{ns}/{name}/lab<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.3
    Gateway->>RBAC: Forward via HTTPRoute<br/>HTTPS/8443, Bearer token (OAuth)
    RBAC->>RBAC: Validate OpenShift RBAC<br/>User must have namespace access
    RBAC->>Jupyter: Proxy to container<br/>HTTP/8888, plaintext (localhost)
    Jupyter-->>RBAC: HTML/WebSocket response
    RBAC-->>Gateway: Encrypted response
    Gateway-->>User: Workbench UI

    Note over Culler,CodeSrv: Flow 3: Idle Culling (Code-Server/RStudio)
    Culler->>RBAC: GET /api/activity<br/>HTTPS/8443, ServiceAccount token
    RBAC->>Nginx: Proxy request<br/>HTTP/80, plaintext
    Nginx->>HTTPD: Forward to CGI<br/>HTTP/8080, plaintext
    HTTPD->>HTTPD: Execute access.cgi script
    HTTPD->>CodeSrv: Check /healthz<br/>HTTP/8787, plaintext
    CodeSrv-->>HTTPD: Health status
    HTTPD-->>Nginx: Activity response
    Nginx-->>RBAC: Activity status
    RBAC-->>Culler: Activity data (idle or active)
